Chinagorom Onuoha, popularly known by his stage name African China, has posted a video on Instagram showing a policeman threatening to shoot him. African China said he had just finished filming a video with another musician, Sound Sultan at Ajegunle before the incident occurred.
The video showed the officer pointing a rifle at the artiste from his windscreen.
“Nigeria see the kind of policemen this Government put on our police station’s to serve dis nation…. After shooting @soundsultan music video in AJ, I was about leaving after given money to Area boys, this… policeman jumped in front of my car and threatened to shoot me…”
